						h2 Our Journey
						p Beehive Drones was founded in 2017 by a group of Indonesian students in the Manchester, United Kingdom who want to bring the power of drones into the field of conventional Industries. The founders believe that in the competitive and fast moving world, efficiency become a crucial aspect and drone is a very powerful tool to achieve that. Today, Beehive Drones produces drone system, IoT sensors, surveillance system, and tracking management systems. Beehive Drones signature swarm drones technology had brought the team to be national champion, Asia Pacific representative, and world finalist in Imagine Cup 2018 by Microsoft.
						p After registered in Indonesia under the name of PT Aerotek Global Inovasi, Beehive Drones team is growing strong and received well by various industries in Indonesia. We work both for private and government sectors, quenching the thirst of industries for innovative, reliable, and affordable advanced technologies.
						p With the motto of 
							b REDEFINING THE POSSIBILITIES
							| , Beehive Drones journey is far from over. Beehive Drones dreams are to assist industries in embracing modern technology, pursue their efficiency goals, and be a trusted partner for Industry Revolution 4.0.
